{"tid":798335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅的司機「唔熟路」誤闖輕鐵路軌 車呔冒煙好驚險","createTime":"2018-08-29T08:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T09:22:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce371e8e8d5f77588ba0ed383bae35f3c20559d3","tid":798335,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535519720_791d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535519720_791d.jpg&h=d8ada5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n的士鏟上輕鐵路軌,司機似一臉茫然。(讀者陳先生提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535519720_cb2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535519720_cb2f.jpg&h=2a964d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535519738_6a65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535519738_6a65.jpg&h=89011027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n噚晚7點幾，市民陳先生行經天水圍鍾屋村輕鐵站對開，見到一部載客紅頂的士，沿青山公路洪水橋段行駛，駛近紫翠花園對開燈位轉綠燈後，本來係轉左，但係的士竟然一支箭咁飊咗去前面，直鏟上去輕鐵路軌，陳先生親眼目睹此情景不禁嘩然，「的士畀路軌啲石仔卡住，佢(的士司機)想倒後出番嚟，唔成功，攪到後面左邊車呔出晒煙！」<br />\n<br />\n陳先生見狀，擔心司機與該名男乘客安全，立即衝上前叫司機落車。「其實當時車上的男乘客已落咗車，佢畀埋車資就離開咗。」他指男乘客笑笑口，表現淡定，並無怪責的士司機。<br />\n<br />\n反而的士司機似不知危險，仍使勁欲倒後的士，「佢剩係一舖蠻力想倒後，我叫佢唔好倒後啦，條呔出晒煙，快啲落車啦！」的士司機才下車，陳先生形容司機當時「唔慌張、呆呆滯滯咁，但對答到」，陳著他不要再倒車，的士司機表示「諗住泊埋一邊」，最後的士司機下車，走到車尾查看車胎損毀程度，此時已嗅到大陣「立青」味，車胎亦磨毀。<br />\n<br />\n此時輕鐵來回方向的列車，因的士塞在路軌而無法開行，當時正值下班時間，乘客頗多，惟列車在中途未能埋站，所以乘客「侷住」在車廂等候。陳先生最後見的士由拖車吊離路軌，列車始恢復行駛，事件擾攘約半小時。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，28號晚上7時39分，姓郭（65歲）司機駕駛載客的士，沿青山公路行駛，其間誤入輕鐵路軌，最後由港鐵職員帶領他離開，事件中沒有人受傷，據悉，有人對警員表示「唔熟路」。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人回覆查詢時表示，28號晚上約7時半，一部的士在輕鐵洪水橋站附近路口，進入輕鐵路軌範圍，不能離開，阻礙該處輕鐵來回線服務，4條輕鐵路線受影響，包括610、614、615、751路線來回方向服務，輕鐵安排公司拖車將的士移離路軌，約7點40分，往元朗輕鐵路軌可回復行車，至7點50分，的士完全被移離路軌，輕鐵服務陸續回復正常。其間個別輕鐵站或輕鐵車廂都有進行廣播，通知乘客最新的輕鐵服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180829/58620216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180829%2F58620216&d=Y6%2BhmZRuZm2cBO01iDldprZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=9d698432\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180829%2F58620216&h=fd42df2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180829/58620216</a>"},{"pid":"e3df6cf68c5883550634d0e1598db4ff6134fb88","tid":798335,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:33:19.000Z","msg":"GTA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380a757594fe7e16dbca7337716da4f00ba0b118","tid":798335,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca405d0708ad5053aa3314dd21d4d55bb0621733","tid":798335,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"呢個明顯係智力問題，唔關熟唔熟事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564b3f17051fc0f12053e53849961125ddd6e88e","tid":798335,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5c1bb224dfbb393fc4eca28b44a90515ab1c80","tid":798335,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:39:08.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5712962ef79419adce65b91345fe4732c94a41af","tid":798335,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"原來鍾屋村都計入天水圍？"}]}